The 13 data files in this Teams directory contain Space station (SST) location data
as a function of time for the entire mission for which EPEE was active. The files
contain 10 columns and (43200) X (Number of Days Per Month) rows.  The 43200 value
derives from the sample rate of EPEE which was one sample for every 2 seconds.

The columns are from left to right :
Year, Month, Day of Month, Day of Year, Hour, Minute, Second, Latitude, Longitude,
Altitude

